<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the following line:</p>

<p>{{$fieldValue = $this-&gt;getName() . '=' . urlencode($this-&gt;getValue());}}</p>

<p>SetCookie::getFieldValue() ignores the fact that cookies may come already encoded (for example from responses). As a result they are double encoded in this method and become invalid.</p>

